\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Overall pipeline of AdaIN StyleKV. Content and style images enter the VAE in parallel; a Canny edge map of the content anchors ControlNet. DDIM inversion produces latent trajectories for both images. Cross-modal AdaIN fuses text and image conditions at the target UNet block, and cached style K/V are blended with content K/V inside selected self-attention processors. The VAE decoder produces the final output.}}{3}{figure.caption.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:pipeline}{{2}{3}{Overall pipeline of AdaIN StyleKV. Content and style images enter the VAE in parallel; a Canny edge map of the content anchors ControlNet. DDIM inversion produces latent trajectories for both images. Cross-modal AdaIN fuses text and image conditions at the target UNet block, and cached style K/V are blended with content K/V inside selected self-attention processors. The VAE decoder produces the final output}{figure.caption.2}{}}
