\newlabel{tab:qual_blocks}{{8}{8}{Qualitative comparison of different target block counts and AdaIN configurations. Configurations using AdaIN exhibit better color coordination and more uniform style coverage; configurations without AdaIN show stronger style transfer but more noticeable content structure degradation}{table.caption.19}{}}
\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {13}{\ignorespaces Impact of the AdaIN module on style transfer (1-block configuration). Top row: results with AdaIN; bottom row: results without AdaIN. The AdaIN module improves color coordination and overall atmospheric consistency, with the difference being more pronounced at higher $\gamma $ values.}}{8}{figure.caption.20}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:adain_compare}{{13}{8}{Impact of the AdaIN module on style transfer (1-block configuration). Top row: results with AdaIN; bottom row: results without AdaIN. The AdaIN module improves color coordination and overall atmospheric consistency, with the difference being more pronounced at higher $\gamma $ values}{figure.caption.20}{}}
